{"article_id":"rerztMDTuSf08sy4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Democratic Senator Elizabeth Warren ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"ridiculed by U.S. President Donald Trump as \" Pocahontas \"","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"for claiming Native American heritage ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"hit back on Monday with DNA evidence","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"she said","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"supported her assertion , a possible preview of a bare-knuckles presidential campaign in 2020 .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The Massachusetts lawmaker ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"known as a liberal firebrand in her party ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"said last month","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"she would take a \" hard look \" at running for the Democratic nomination","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to challenge Republican Trump in 2020 .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"She and Trump clashed frequently through the 2016 presidential campaign","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and Trump has cast aspersions on her claim to Native American ancestry .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"\" When I decided to run for Senate in 2012 ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"I never thought","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"that my family ' s Native American heritage would come under attack","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"and my dead parents would be called liars , \"","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"she said in a statement on Monday .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"\" And I never expected the president of the United States to use my family ' s story as a racist political joke , \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Trump taunted Warren over the issue at a July rally in Montana .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"\" I will give you a million dollars to your favorite charity ,","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"paid for by Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"if you take the test","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"and it shows","depth":15},{"id":26,"text":"you ' re an Indian , \"","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"\" I have a feeling","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"she will say ' no . ' \"","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"Warren reminded the president on Monday of his promise .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"\" Please send the check to the National Indigenous Women ' s Resource Center , \"","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"she said on Twitter .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"When asked about the DNA test ,","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"Trump said :","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"\" Who cares ? \"","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"Then he denied making the comment ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"as he left Washington","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"to visit hurricane-stricken areas in Florida and Georgia .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"Later , Trump suggested to reporters in Georgia","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"he could pay the $ 1 million","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"he had wagered ,","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"but with a caveat :","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"\" I ' ll only do it","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"if I can test her personally .","depth":15},{"id":45,"text":"That will not be something","depth":15},{"id":46,"text":"I will enjoy doing either , \"","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"Trump ' s use of the name Pocahontas refers to a 17th century Native American woman","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"associated with the British colony in Jamestown , Virginia ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"and was aimed at drawing attention to a controversy over her heritage","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"raised during Warren ' s 2012 Senate race .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"Trump ' s mocking reference has drawn criticism from Native American groups .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Warren provided the DNA test results in a statement ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"showing","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"the lineage goes back six to 10 generations .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"bit.ly/2OqLmUz","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"The analysis of Warren ' s DNA was done by Carlos Bustamante , a Stanford University professor","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"whom","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"the Boston Globe reported","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"was an expert in the field .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"The professor concluded","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"that most of the senator ' s DNA showed European ancestry","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"but that it had a Native American segment .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Warren has said","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that her Native American ancestry possibly goes back to the 1700s ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"including Cherokee blood on her mother ' s side ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"according to family lore .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Warren ' s release of the results was criticized by Cherokee Nation Secretary of State Chuck Hoskin Jr. ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"who said ;","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"\" Using a DNA test","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"to lay claim to any connection to the Cherokee Nation or any tribal nation , even vaguely , is inappropriate and wrong . \"","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Warren ' s move could be a prelude to a possible presidential run .","depth":4},{"id":73,"text":"An architect of the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"set up after the 2008 financial crisis ,","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Warren has been a strong voice in the U.S. Senate on financial issues .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"Warren ,","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"campaigning with Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton in 2016 ,","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"attacked Trump as an \" insecure money grubber \"","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"driven by greed and hate .","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"\" I hope","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"she ' s running for president ,","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"because I think","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"she ' ll be very easy , \"","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Trump said","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"as he left the White House on Monday .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":171,"left":0,"right":170,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":170,"left":157,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":137,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":91,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":88,"right":90,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":88,"left":1,"right":87,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":4,"right":89,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":136,"left":95,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":93,"right":94,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":92,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":96,"right":134,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":134,"left":102,"right":133,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":100,"right":101,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":14,"right":98,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":15,"right":97,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":113,"right":132,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":110,"right":112,"relation":"adversa